"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-raygun-revenge-australian-breakdancer-tops-world-rankings-latest\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.7918471026244148, \"rank\": 0.26268706668416564, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbRaygun's revenge: Australian breakdancer tops world rankings  Australian Olympic breakdancer \\\"Raygun\\\" has been ridiculed, written off - and now crowned number one in the world.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.7918471026244148, \"rank\": 0.26268706668416564, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 222, \"end\": 232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9698491931787023, \"rank\": 0.02918043372755228, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 266, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9698491931787023, \"rank\": 0.02918043372755228, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Olympic breakdancer \\\"Raygun\\\" has been ridiculed, written off, and now crownednumber one in the world, the sport's governing body confirmed on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9698491931787023, \"rank\": 0.02918043372755228, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rachael \\\"Raygun\\\" Gunn, 37, became something of a global laughing stock after her kangaroo-inspired routine failed to impress the judges at theParis Olympics, where the sport of breaking made its debut.\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 547, \"end\": 554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 2.8911281168886768e-12, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.733473035264865e-29, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999964858696231, \"rank\": 2.0176909086423163e-06, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her moves were parodied on late-night talk shows, her unfashionable tracksuit was lampooned online and breaking aficionados around the world questioned how she had made the team.\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Raygun got her revenge and the last laugh when the World Dance Sport Federation (WDSF) named her the number one female breakdancer in the world.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rankings were based on the athlete's four top performances within the past 12 months, said the WDSF on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, with few ranking events held between December 2023 and the Olympics, \\\"many athletes have only one competition result contributing to their ranking,\\\" a WDSF statement said.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1359, \"end\": 1363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn won the Oceania Continental Championship in that period, earning her 1000 ranking points.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1381, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999964858696231, \"rank\": 2.0176909086423163e-06, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\", \"score\": 0.9999586554934112, \"rank\": 4.110102200971636e-05, \"text\": \"Oceania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japanese B-girl Riko's win at the Gold World Series in Hong Kong in December 2023 saw her also awarded 1000 points, but the WDSF said Raygun's event carried more weight, so awarded her the top ranking.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9968844485958461, \"rank\": 0.002143198601934132, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9899438614176085, \"rank\": 0.010158012312970296, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}, {\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 1611, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.733473035264865e-29, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Raygun's reign at the top could be short-lived.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1680, \"end\": 1686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.733473035264865e-29, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The WDSF confirms that rankings will change after the 12-month points expire, and when the next WDSF Breaking for Gold World Series is held in Shanghai in October 2024,\\\" the statement added.\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1873, \"end\": 1881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"score\": 0.9999999967531039, \"rank\": 1.7052308349592843e-09, \"text\": \"Shanghai\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The WDSF said it remained \\\"steadfast in its commitment to transparency and fairness\\\" in the competitive ranking process.\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1926, \"end\": 1930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn, a university lecturer, appeared on Australian TV last week to apologise for stirring up a backlash against the wider breakdancing community.\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2044, \"end\": 2048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999964858696231, \"rank\": 2.0176909086423163e-06, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 2085, \"end\": 2095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9698491931787023, \"rank\": 0.02918043372755228, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn said she had not expected to do well at the Olympics, but that her record showed she was the best breaker in Australia.\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2192, \"end\": 2196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999964858696231, \"rank\": 2.0176909086423163e-06, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 2306, \"end\": 2315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9939352285103874, \"rank\": 0.005906250842719512, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As soon as I qualified, I was like, oh my gosh, what have I done?\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because I knew that I was going to get beaten, and I knew that people were not going to understand my style and what I was going to do,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I am very sorry for the backlash that the community has experienced, but I can not control how people react.\\\"\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn had previously spoken out against the \\\"pretty devastating\\\" hatred unleashed after the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2649, \"end\": 2653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999964858696231, \"rank\": 2.0176909086423163e-06, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went out there and I had fun.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did take it very seriously.\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I worked my butt off preparing for the Olympics and I gave my all,\\\" she said in a video message last month.\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While many ridiculed her performance on social media, Gunn won support from others, including her fellow Australian Olympians and Australia's prime minister.\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 3080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2977, \"end\": 2981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999964858696231, \"rank\": 2.0176909086423163e-06, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 3028, \"end\": 3038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9698491931787023, \"rank\": 0.02918043372755228, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 3053, \"end\": 3062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9939352285103874, \"rank\": 0.005906250842719512, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By Garrin Lambley \\u00a9 Agence France-Presse  WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3092, \"end\": 3099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lambley_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.951440538809509, \"rank\": 0.0510376710647838, \"text\": \"Lambley\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lambley_railway_station\